      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MY WEE LASS (1) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 2.5 lengths second (23.13) over 400m at this track. Top prospect. QUEEN LOCH (8) was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by 5 lengths (17.48) at Taree Super Track. Bold showing expected again. DON'T DO IT (6) ran well two back scoring a Grade 5 win in 16.05 then out of the placings at this track latest but returns to a distance over which he has performed well. Expected to bounce back to best. ANOTHER ARTIST (5) has merit but will need to be at her best to take this out.",
